<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs ma! pim ʋlla yʋno
 Ish i̱ hoyullashke;
 Chim anumpa holitopa
 Ish anukfokashke.

[V2]
 Nitak hullo nitak moma,
 Itʋnaha pullʋt,
 Chi̱ holisso holitopa
 Pisʋt aiashashke.

[V3]
 Chi Shilombish achukma ya̱
 Ish ema pullashke;
 Chu̱kʋsh himona ai a̱hli
 Ish im ihi̱kbashke.

[V4]
 Nitak hullo holitobli,
 Holisso pihisa,
 Ataloa taloho̱wʋt
 Aiasha pullashke.

[V5]
 Chisʋs oka i̱ yimmi hosh
 Ʋba yakni hoyot,
 Aiokcha̱yʋt bilia ya̱
 Ahnit taloashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs ma! pim ʋlla yʋno</aka>
<time_sig>C.M. (8.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Sabbath School ƲIT152</title>
<author>Cyrus Byington</author>
<hymn_number>152</hymn_number>
</song>